item.title: Snoop Dogg’s Gin & Juice Brand Becomes Presenting Sponsor of Arizona Bowl
item.description: The Arizona Bowl announced a multi-year partnership with 17-time Grammy Award winning artist Snoop Dogg that makes his alcohol brand, Gin & Juice by Dre and Snoop, the game’s presenting sponsor.
